data.description:
Back on market buyers couldn't qualify for loan. Short sale opportunity. Like new construction. Home is in immaculate shape with upgrades. Value and uniqueness presents itself for your buyers, with this home. NO BUILDER WAIT TIMES.
Smart home. Front yard watering system in place and backyard all hardscaped low maintenance with pavers for seating and entertaining and artificial turf. Park behind home and no 2 story neighbors on any sides, very private lot. Close to fun and shopping. Try Fatcats right down the street for bowling, movies, game arcade and other events. Home-goods, Safeway and Fry's located just a few minutes from home!
